Thanks for reading The Backstory, your weekly capsule of the best work eman=
ating from Puck. It was yet another fabulous week: Matt Belloni and Lesley =
Goldberg compiled the worst showrunner deals of the streaming age; Dylan By=
ers explored an ABC News plot twist; Eriq Gardner unearthed a bizarre CAA l=
egal battle; Lauren Sherman chatted with Tory Burch; Rachel Strugatz exhume=
d the Est=C3=A9e Lauder executive exodus.

